data.description: Welcome to 1647 Ridge Ave, a charming and timeless gem. This meticulously maintained property boasts a perfect blend of modern upgrades and classic features, making it the ideal home for those seeking both comfort and style. Step inside and be greeted by the warm ambiance of refinished hardwood floors, which exude a sense of elegance and sophistication. The spacious living area offers a cozy retreat, perfect for relaxing with loved ones or entertaining guests. The updated HVAC system ensures year-round comfort, allowing you to enjoy the perfect temperature no matter the season 2022. Whip up culinary masterpieces while enjoying the natural light that floods the space, creating an inviting atmosphere for culinary creativity. The three bedrooms provide a peaceful sanctuary, each offering ample space and storage. Outside, the roof, replaced in 2016, offers peace of mind and protection from the elements. The hot water heater, recently installed in 2022, ensures a constant supply of warm water for your comfort. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property is just moments away from Daytona Beach's finest attractions, including pristine beaches, vibrant restaurants, and exciting entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your forever home.  All information is deemed to be accurate but not guaranteed
